    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a driver-focused example featuring the high-revving S54B32 inline-six powerplant, renowned for its individual throttle bodies and 8,000 RPM redline. The mechanical synchronization of the Getrag 6-speed manual transmission and the factory limited-slip differential provides an analog driving experience increasingly rare in modern segments. This chassis has undergone a comprehensive subframe reinforcement and a recent double VANOS service to ensure optimal cam timing and torque delivery. Suspension geometry remains true with refreshed bushings, offering the precise turn-in and balanced weight distribution characteristic of the M-division's engineering. A mechanically sound specimen for the purist who values visceral feedback and Bavarian performance heritage.",
      "price": 34500.0,
